short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Click to call extension for your CRMs and Tools

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:

For more information about the supported integrations, please check https://toky.co/en/integrations.
